      { question: "What is train-of-four monitoring?", answer: "TOF monitoring uses a nerve stimulator to deliver four electrical stimuli to a peripheral nerve. The number of muscle twitches (0–4) indicates the degree of neuromuscular blockade. Target is 1–2/4 for ICU paralysis." }
